<p style="text-align:center"><strong>$3.50 per ounce.</strong> Same price for every <a href="/greens/">variety</a>. Free delivery in our <a href="/delivery/">service zones</a>.</p>

<p>Most households start with 2–4oz per week. A 2oz portion tops salads, eggs, sandwiches, and tacos for a family of four for several days. Stored in the fridge in their clamshell, they stay fresh about 7 days from harvest. Standing weekly orders <a href="/subscribe/">save 10%</a>.</p>

