<h2>Payment & delivery</h2>

<p><strong>Pay on delivery.</strong> Venmo, Zelle, or cash — whatever's easiest. We text you the total the day before so there are no surprises.</p>

<p><strong>No subscription, no auto-charge.</strong> Order any week you want, skip any week you don't. We'll text you each week to confirm your standing order or to ask if you'd like something new.</p>

<p><strong>Free delivery</strong> within our service neighborhoods: Lake Mary, Sanford, Winter Springs, Oviedo, Casselberry, Maitland, Winter Park, College Park, and Downtown Orlando. <a href="/microgreens/">See the full schedule and place an order →</a></p>

